review_title: Cute way of showing a short story
one_reviews_text: It's like a popup book in VR. Not much to it, but I could see it being entertaining to smaller kids.

review_title: Nice VR story experience for kids
one_reviews_text: The graphics are not the best. The story would probably be more enjoyable for kids.  There are no interactions. The voice acting was the best thing about this experience. Whole thing is about 6-7 minutes long. Not something I would show off to friends or family, but not bad.
